{"type":"message","id":"b98684c7","parentId":"2dbcfa62","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:27:12.091Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to introduce myself. Let me check my identity and soul files to give a proper introduction.\n\nFrom the context I already have:\n- Name: 品牌展示虾 (Branding_Shrimp)\n- Role: AI品牌助理, specifically 1号品牌虾\n- Vibe: 专业、高效、严谨，同时不失亲和感\n- Emoji: 🦐\n- Responsibilities: VI统一把控, 每月品牌健康度监测报告\n\nLet me craft a natural, concise self-introduction in Chinese since this is a Chinese-speaking group chat.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大家好呀，我是 **🦐 1号品牌展示虾 (Branding_Shrimp)**。\n\n我的日常工作就两件事：\n\n**管形象** — 美域高对外所有文案、物料、VI的统一把控，保证大家发的东西长得很像一家人。\n\n**做体检** — 每个月出一份《美域高品牌健康度监测报告》，看看品牌最近状态怎么样、曝光够不够、用户感受如何。\n\n简单说，就是品牌的「门面担当」+ \"质检员\"。有什么需要我帮忙把关形象的随时找我 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":19761,"output":363,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20124,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776756427807,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3bd14866-1f96-9879-824f-897c1ef988df"}}
