{"type":"message","id":"148dbba0","parentId":"842efd39","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:29:45.024Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_994c067a83f54cdfbbf5ec77","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: \"multi-search-engine\"\ndescription: \"【国内精简版】多种免费搜索方式在互联网上搜索最新信息，10个国内网站（精简7个国内不能访问的海外网站）\"\n---\n\n# Multi Search Engine\n\n集成 10 个免费搜索引擎。\n\n## Search Engines\n\n- **Baidu**: `https://www.baidu.com/s?wd={keyword}`\n- **Bing CN**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=0`\n- **Bing INT**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=1`\n- **360**: `https://www.so.com/s?q={keyword}`\n- **Sogou**: `https://sogou.com/web?query={keyword}`\n- **WeChat**: `https://wx.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&query={keyword}`\n- **Toutiao**: `https://so.toutiao.com/search?keyword={keyword}`\n- **Jisilu**: `https://www.jisilu.cn/explore/?keyword={keyword}`\n- **Ecosia**: `https://www.ecosia.org/search?q={keyword}`\n- **WolframAlpha**: `https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i={keyword}`\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776756585023}}
{"type":"message","id":"00aff10b","parentId":"148dbba0","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:29:46.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So this is a skill for searching via multiple engines. But I need to figure out how to actually use it - does it have a CLI or script? Let me check the README and config.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b951243519ac492596000f40","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multi-search-engine-simple/README.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c9e0195fedc94efba6795402","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multi-search-engine-simple/config.json"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":22341,"output":159,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22500,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776756585025,"responseId":"chatcmpl-edc16b94-d975-98f0-9ab8-eaf2a2537597"}}
{"type":"message","id":"92ed666a","parentId":"00aff10b","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:29:46.222Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b951243519ac492596000f40","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Multi Search Engine\n\n## 说明\n\n- 精简了没有梯子访问不了的7个网站，防止大模型乱试。\n- 大模型大概率只会随机挑选一个渠道，如果访问成功就不会进行下一次请求了，并非所有搜索引擎的结果聚合。\n\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776756586222}}
{"type":"message","id":"68f16228","parentId":"92ed666a","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:29:46.223Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c9e0195fedc94efba6795402","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"name\": \"multi-search-engine\",\n  \"engines\": [\n    {\"name\": \"Baidu\", \"url\": \"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd={keyword}\", \"region\": \"cn\"},\n    {\"name\": \"Bing CN\", \"url\": \"https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=0\", \"region\": \"cn\"},\n    {\"name\": \"Bing INT\", \"url\": \"https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=1\", \"region\": \"global\"},\n    {\"name\": \"360\", \"url\": \"https://www.so.com/s?q={keyword}\", \"region\": \"cn\"},\n    {\"name\": \"Sogou\", \"url\": \"https://sogou.com/web?query={keyword}\", \"region\": \"cn\"},\n    {\"name\": \"WeChat\", \"url\": \"https://wx.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&query={keyword}\", \"region\": \"cn\"},\n    {\"name\": \"Toutiao\", \"url\": \"https://so.toutiao.com/search?keyword={keyword}\", \"region\": \"cn\"},\n    {\"name\": \"Jisilu\", \"url\": \"https://www.jisilu.cn/explore/?keyword={keyword}\", \"region\": \"cn\"},\n    {\"name\": \"Ecosia\", \"url\": \"https://www.ecosia.org/search?q={keyword}\", \"region\": \"global\"},\n    {\"name\": \"WolframAlpha\", \"url\": \"https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i={keyword}\", \"region\": \"global\"}\n  ]\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776756586223}}
{"type":"message","id":"f466ebab","parentId":"68f16228","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:29:52.739Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This skill is just a set of search URLs to use with `web_fetch`. It doesn't have a standalone CLI. I need to use `web_fetch` to fetch these search engine result pages and parse them.\n\nThe README says \"大模型大概率只会随机挑选一个渠道，如果访问成功就不会进行下一次请求了\" - meaning the LLM should pick one engine.\n\nLet me now search for information about each shrimp role using multiple engines. I'll construct appropriate search queries and use web_fetch.\n\nActually, wait - let me re-read the user's request: \"使用multi-search-engine-simple搜索关于你们工作职位的信息，然后学习，理解，记忆！\"\n\n\nI've already got the team structure from memory—0是总经理, 1 is brand display (me), 2 does lead generation, 3 handles short videos, 4A manages regular sales, 4B handles key accounts, 5A processes standard applications, 5B handles key account applications, and so on. The user wants me to use multi-search-engine-simple to gather more detailed job descriptions and information about each position.\n\nI'll go ahead and run searches across Baidu and Bing CN for each role title to find comprehensive details about what these positions entail.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来用 multi-search-engine-simple 搜索引擎查找我们各个岗位的具体职责信息。先批量搜一下所有角色：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_af26c278f2d4468ea09704dc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== Searching roles ===\" && echo \"--- Baidu ---\" && curl -sL \"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=美域高+品牌展示虾+岗位职责\" -H \"User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0\" | head -c 2000 > /tmp/search_baidu.txt && wc -c /tmp/search_baidu.txt && echo \"--- Bing CN ---\" && curl -sL \"https://cn.bing.com/search?q=美域高+团队+岗位+职责&ensearch=0\" -H \"User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0\" | head -c 2000 > /tmp/search_bing.txt && wc -c /tmp/search_bing.txt && echo \"--- Sogou ---\" && curl -sL \"https://sogou.com/web?query=美域高+AI+团队+岗位+分工\" -H \"User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0\" | head -c 2000 > /tmp/search_sogou.txt && wc -c /tmp/search_sogou.txt && echo \"--- 360 ---\" && curl -sL \"https://www.so.com/s?q=美域高+虾+团队+职责\" -H \"User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0\" | head -c 2000 > /tmp/search_360.txt && wc -c /tmp/search_360.txt","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":22890,"output":881,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23771,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776756586224,"responseId":"chatcmpl-23025024-f0ef-9f91-a86c-42d346cd1d13"}}
